data.eml:eml: Foraminifera study in the Lysefjord and Høgsfjord, western Norway

Occurrence data of living benthic foraminifera in the Høgsfjord, collected in 2013. Samples were taken with a gravity corer. The data represent the occurrence of living benthic foraminifera (>63µm) in the upper sediment centimeter (0-1cm) of 3 replicates.
